#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.between.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.between"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.between.between:1 of
msgid ""
"Return boolean Series equivalent to left <= series <= right. This "
"function returns a boolean vector containing `True` wherever the "
"corresponding Series element is between the boundary values `left` and "
"`right`. NA values are treated as `False`."
msgstr ""
"返回一个布尔 Series，等价于 left <= series <= right。此函数返回一个布尔"
"向量，其中对应 Series 元素在边界值 `left` 和 `right` 之间时为 `True`。NA "
"值被视为 `False`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.between.between of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.between.between:6 of
msgid "Left boundary."
msgstr "左边界。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.between.between:8 of
msgid "Right boundary."
msgstr "右边界。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.between.between:10 of
msgid "Include boundaries. Whether to set each bound as closed or open."
msgstr "是否包含边界。设置每个边界是闭合还是开放。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.between.between of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.between.between:13 of
msgid ""
"Series representing whether each element is between left and right "
"(inclusive)."
msgstr "表示每个元素是否在 left 和 right 之间（包含）的 Series。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.between.between of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.between.between:19 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.gt`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.between.between:20 of
msgid "Greater than of series and other."
msgstr "Series 与 other 的大于比较。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.between.between:22 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.lt`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.between.between:23 of
msgid "Less than of series and other."
msgstr "Series 与 other 的小于比较。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.between.between:26 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.between.between:27 of
msgid "This function is equivalent to ``(left <= ser) & (ser <= right)``"
msgstr "此函数等价于 ``(left <= ser) & (ser <= right)``"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.between.between:30 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.between.between:34 of
msgid "Boundary values are included by default:"
msgstr "默认情况下包含边界值："

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.between.between:44 of
msgid "With `inclusive` set to ``\"neither\"`` boundary values are excluded:"
msgstr "当 `inclusive` 设置为 ``\"neither\"`` 时，边界值被排除："

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.between.between:54 of
msgid "`left` and `right` can be any scalar value:"
msgstr "`left` 和 `right` 可以是任意标量值："

